name: Faith in the Chaos of the World
description:
Most people believe in one religion and some do not. But in everyone's heart must have faith and belief in one thing, be it god, satan or themselves. It is the faith they hold to face the chaos of the world.

The cross is just a symbol of faith itself. Because its form can be represented in many forms and even intangibles.

This photo was taken at one of the churches in Ciamis, Indonesia in 2018.
